{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":444,"text":"I think I'll start out\nand just talk a little bit"},{"time":2914,"text":"about what exactly autism is."},{"time":4429,"text":"Autism is a very big continuum"},{"time":7088,"text":"that goes from very severe --\nthe child remains nonverbal --"},{"time":10286,"text":"all the way up to brilliant\nscientists and engineers."},{"time":13000,"text":"And I actually feel at home here,"},{"time":15001,"text":"because there's a lot\nof autism genetics here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17571,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":18627,"text":"You wouldn't have any --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":19809,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":22802,"text":"It's a continuum of traits."},{"time":24862,"text":"When does a nerd turn into Asperger,\nwhich is just mild autism?"},{"time":30543,"text":"I mean, Einstein and Mozart and Tesla\nwould all be probably diagnosed"},{"time":35725,"text":"as autistic spectrum today."},{"time":37641,"text":"And one of the things\nthat is really going to concern me"},{"time":40956,"text":"is getting these kids to be the ones"},{"time":43215,"text":"that are going to invent\nthe next energy things"},{"time":46061,"text":"that Bill Gates talked about this morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48798,"text":"OK, now, if you want\nto understand autism: animals."},{"time":52735,"text":"I want to talk to you now\nabout different ways of thinking."},{"time":55649,"text":"You have to get away from verbal language."},{"time":58523,"text":"I think in pictures.\nI don't think in language."},{"time":62822,"text":"Now, the thing about the autistic mind\nis it attends to details."},{"time":68116,"text":"This is a test where you either\nhave to pick out the big letters"},{"time":71195,"text":"or the little letters,"},{"time":72442,"text":"and the autistic mind picks out\nthe little letters more quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76687,"text":"And the thing is, the normal brain\nignores the details."},{"time":80462,"text":"Well, if you're building a bridge,\ndetails are pretty important"},{"time":83496,"text":"because it'll fall down\nif you ignore the details."},{"time":85918,"text":"And one of my big concerns\nwith a lot of policy things today"},{"time":88809,"text":"is things are getting too abstract."},{"time":90511,"text":"People are getting away\nfrom doing hands-on stuff."},{"time":93762,"text":"I'm really concerned\nthat a lot of the schools"},{"time":95946,"text":"have taken out the hands-on classes,\nbecause art, and classes like that --"},{"time":99938,"text":"those are the classes where I excelled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102275,"text":"In my work with cattle,"},{"time":104453,"text":"I noticed a lot of little things\nthat most people don't notice"},{"time":107455,"text":"would make the cattle balk."},{"time":108767,"text":"For example, this flag waving\nright in front of the veterinary facility."},{"time":112338,"text":"This feed yard was going to tear down\ntheir whole veterinary facility;"},{"time":115689,"text":"all they needed to do was move the flag."},{"time":117627,"text":"Rapid movement, contrast."},{"time":119719,"text":"In the early '70s when I started,\nI got right down in the chutes"},{"time":122777,"text":"to see what cattle were seeing."},{"time":124300,"text":"People thought that was crazy."},{"time":125786,"text":"A coat on a fence would make them balk,\nshadows would make them balk,"},{"time":129092,"text":"a hose on the floor --\npeople weren't noticing these things."},{"time":132180,"text":"A chain hanging down ..."},{"time":133720,"text":"And that's shown\nvery, very nicely in the movie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"In fact, I loved the movie,\nhow they duplicated all my projects."},{"time":139479,"text":"That's the geek side."},{"time":140844,"text":"My drawings got to star in the movie, too."},{"time":143288,"text":"And, actually, it's called\n\"Temple Grandin,\""},{"time":145422,"text":"not \"Thinking in Pictures.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":146770,"text":"So what is thinking in pictures?"},{"time":148359,"text":"It's literally movies in your head."},{"time":151062,"text":"My mind works like Google for images."},{"time":153968,"text":"When I was a young kid,\nI didn't know my thinking was different."},{"time":157036,"text":"I thought everybody thought in pictures."},{"time":158979,"text":"Then when I did my book,\n\"Thinking in Pictures,\""},{"time":161258,"text":"I started interviewing people\nabout how they think."},{"time":163694,"text":"And I was shocked to find out\nthat my thinking was quite different."},{"time":166873,"text":"Like if I say, \"Think\nabout a church steeple,\""},{"time":169073,"text":"most people get this sort\nof generalized generic one."},{"time":171610,"text":"Now, maybe that's not true in this room,"},{"time":173546,"text":"but it's going to be true\nin a lot of different places."},{"time":176836,"text":"I see only specific pictures."},{"time":179363,"text":"They flash up into my memory,\njust like Google for pictures."},{"time":183196,"text":"And in the movie,\nthey've got a great scene in there,"},{"time":185763,"text":"where the word \"shoe\" is said,\nand a whole bunch of '50s and '60s shoes"},{"time":189587,"text":"pop into my imagination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191648,"text":"OK, there's my childhood church;\nthat's specific."},{"time":194547,"text":"There's some more, Fort Collins."},{"time":196439,"text":"OK, how about famous ones?"},{"time":198510,"text":"And they just kind of come up,\nkind of like this."},{"time":201211,"text":"Just really quickly,\nlike Google for pictures."},{"time":204146,"text":"And they come up one at a time,"},{"time":205729,"text":"and then I think, \"OK, well,\nmaybe we can have it snow,"},{"time":208704,"text":"or we can have a thunderstorm,\""},{"time":210352,"text":"and I can hold it there\nand turn them into videos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"Now, visual thinking\nwas a tremendous asset"},{"time":216237,"text":"in my work designing\ncattle-handling facilities."},{"time":219539,"text":"And I've worked really hard\non improving how cattle are treated"},{"time":222763,"text":"at the slaughter plant."},{"time":223939,"text":"I'm not going to go\ninto any gucky slaughter slides."},{"time":226459,"text":"I've got that stuff up on YouTube,\nif you want to look at it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229371,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":230436,"text":"But one of the things\nthat I was able to do in my design work"},{"time":233353,"text":"is I could test-run a piece\nof equipment in my mind,"},{"time":236000,"text":"just like a virtual reality\ncomputer system."},{"time":239448,"text":"And this is an aerial view\nof a recreation of one of my projects"},{"time":243113,"text":"that was used in the movie."},{"time":244499,"text":"That was like just so super cool."},{"time":246534,"text":"And there were a lot of, kind of,\nAsperger types and autism types"},{"time":250036,"text":"working out there on the movie set, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252008,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253208,"text":"But one of the things\nthat really worries me is:"},{"time":256023,"text":"Where's the younger version\nof those kids going today?"},{"time":259560,"text":"They're not ending up in Silicon Valley,"},{"time":262039,"text":"where they belong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263303,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":265147,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270079,"text":"One of the things I learned very early on\nbecause I wasn't that social,"},{"time":273684,"text":"is I had to sell my work, and not myself."},{"time":277446,"text":"And the way I sold livestock jobs\nis I showed off my drawings,"},{"time":280430,"text":"I showed off pictures of things."},{"time":282186,"text":"Another thing that helped me\nas a little kid"},{"time":284449,"text":"is, boy, in the '50s,\nyou were taught manners."},{"time":286702,"text":"You were taught you can't pull\nthe merchandise off the shelves"},{"time":289765,"text":"in the store and throw it around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291423,"text":"When kids get to be\nin third or fourth grade,"},{"time":293599,"text":"you might see that this kid's going\nto be a visual thinker,"},{"time":296451,"text":"drawing in perspective."},{"time":297740,"text":"Now, I want to emphasize"},{"time":298962,"text":"that not every autistic kid\nis going to be a visual thinker."},{"time":302452,"text":"Now, I had this brain scan\ndone several years ago,"},{"time":306454,"text":"and I used to joke around about having\na gigantic Internet trunk line"},{"time":310411,"text":"going deep into my visual cortex."},{"time":312362,"text":"This is tensor imaging."},{"time":314261,"text":"And my great big Internet trunk line\nis twice as big as the control's."},{"time":318137,"text":"The red lines there are me,"},{"time":319765,"text":"and the blue lines are the sex\nand age-matched control."},{"time":324590,"text":"And there I got a gigantic one,"},{"time":326636,"text":"and the control over there, the blue one,\nhas got a really small one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331841,"text":"And some of the research now is showing"},{"time":334000,"text":"that people on the spectrum actually\nthink with the primary visual cortex."},{"time":338055,"text":"Now, the thing is, the visual thinker\nis just one kind of mind."},{"time":341120,"text":"You see, the autistic mind\ntends to be a specialist mind --"},{"time":344729,"text":"good at one thing, bad at something else."},{"time":347842,"text":"And where I was bad was algebra."},{"time":349620,"text":"And I was never allowed\nto take geometry or trig."},{"time":351934,"text":"Gigantic mistake."},{"time":353121,"text":"I'm finding a lot of kids\nwho need to skip algebra,"},{"time":355580,"text":"go right to geometry and trig."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357587,"text":"Now, another kind of mind\nis the pattern thinker."},{"time":360211,"text":"More abstract."},{"time":361474,"text":"These are your engineers,\nyour computer programmers."},{"time":364061,"text":"This is pattern thinking."},{"time":365479,"text":"That praying mantis is made\nfrom a single sheet of paper --"},{"time":368388,"text":"no scotch tape, no cuts."},{"time":369829,"text":"And there in the background\nis the pattern for folding it."},{"time":373388,"text":"Here are the types of thinking:"},{"time":375471,"text":"photo-realistic visual thinkers, like me;"},{"time":378596,"text":"pattern thinkers, music and math minds."},{"time":382000,"text":"Some of these oftentimes\nhave problems with reading."},{"time":384612,"text":"You also will see these kind of problems\nwith kids that are dyslexic."},{"time":389117,"text":"You'll see these different kinds of minds."},{"time":391165,"text":"And then there's a verbal mind,\nthey know every fact about everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394763,"text":"Now, another thing is the sensory issues."},{"time":396753,"text":"I was really concerned about having\nto wear this gadget on my face."},{"time":400432,"text":"And I came in half an hour beforehand"},{"time":402610,"text":"so I could have it put on\nand kind of get used to it,"},{"time":405617,"text":"and they got it bent\nso it's not hitting my chin."},{"time":408379,"text":"But sensory is an issue."},{"time":409555,"text":"Some kids are bothered\nby fluorescent lights;"},{"time":411728,"text":"others have problems\nwith sound sensitivity."},{"time":414237,"text":"You know, it's going to be variable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417392,"text":"Now, visual thinking gave me\na whole lot of insight"},{"time":420836,"text":"into the animal mind."},{"time":423120,"text":"Because think about it:\nan animal is a sensory-based thinker,"},{"time":426577,"text":"not verbal -- thinks in pictures,\nthinks in sounds, thinks in smells."},{"time":432798,"text":"Think about how much information\nthere is on the local fire hydrant."},{"time":436166,"text":"He knows who's been there --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":437552,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":438607,"text":"When they were there."},{"time":439788,"text":"Are they friend or foe?\nIs there anybody he can go mate with?"},{"time":442707,"text":"There's a ton of information\non that fire hydrant."},{"time":445613,"text":"It's all very detailed information."},{"time":448736,"text":"And looking at these kind of details\ngave me a lot of insight into animals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453428,"text":"Now, the animal mind, and also my mind,"},{"time":457000,"text":"puts sensory-based information\ninto categories."},{"time":461593,"text":"Man on a horse,"},{"time":463320,"text":"and a man on the ground --"},{"time":464899,"text":"that is viewed as two\ntotally different things."},{"time":467708,"text":"You could have a horse\nthat's been abused by a rider."},{"time":470231,"text":"They'll be absolutely fine\nwith the veterinarian"},{"time":472525,"text":"and with the horseshoer,\nbut you can't ride him."},{"time":475000,"text":"You have another horse,\nwhere maybe the horseshoer beat him up,"},{"time":478199,"text":"and he'll be terrible for anything\non the ground with the veterinarian,"},{"time":482218,"text":"but a person can ride him."},{"time":484257,"text":"Cattle are the same way."},{"time":485588,"text":"Man on a horse, a man on foot --\nthey're two different things."},{"time":489537,"text":"You see, it's a different picture."},{"time":491517,"text":"See, I want you to think\nabout just how specific this is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494662,"text":"Now, this ability to put\ninformation into categories,"},{"time":498073,"text":"I find a lot of people\nare not very good at this."},{"time":501449,"text":"When I'm out troubleshooting equipment"},{"time":503641,"text":"or problems with something in a plant,"},{"time":505493,"text":"they don't seem to be able to figure out:"},{"time":507522,"text":"\"Do I have a training-people issue?"},{"time":509246,"text":"Or do I have something wrong\nwith the equipment?\""},{"time":511705,"text":"In other words, categorize\nequipment problem from a people problem."},{"time":515423,"text":"I find a lot of people\nhave difficulty doing that."},{"time":518543,"text":"Now, let's say I figure out\nit's an equipment problem."},{"time":521131,"text":"Is it a minor problem,\nwith something simple I can fix?"},{"time":523931,"text":"Or is the whole design\nof the system wrong?"},{"time":526270,"text":"People have a hard time figuring that out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"Let's just look at something\nlike, you know,"},{"time":531120,"text":"solving problems with making\nairlines safer."},{"time":533390,"text":"Yeah, I'm a million-mile flier."},{"time":535000,"text":"I do lots and lots of flying,"},{"time":536850,"text":"and if I was at the FAA,"},{"time":540106,"text":"what would I be doing a lot\nof direct observation of?"},{"time":544197,"text":"It would be their airplane tails."},{"time":546525,"text":"You know, five fatal wrecks\nin the last 20 years,"},{"time":549099,"text":"the tail either came off,"},{"time":550898,"text":"or steering stuff inside the tail\nbroke in some way."},{"time":554747,"text":"It's tails, pure and simple."},{"time":556824,"text":"And when the pilots walk\naround the plane, guess what?"},{"time":559381,"text":"They can't see that stuff inside the tail."},{"time":561456,"text":"Now as I think about that,"},{"time":562917,"text":"I'm pulling up all of that\nspecific information."},{"time":566400,"text":"It's specific."},{"time":567597,"text":"See, my thinking's bottom-up."},{"time":569116,"text":"I take all the little pieces and I put\nthe pieces together like a puzzle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":572837,"text":"Now, here is a horse that was deathly\nafraid of black cowboy hats."},{"time":576628,"text":"He'd been abused by somebody\nwith a black cowboy hat."},{"time":579212,"text":"White cowboy hats,\nthat was absolutely fine."},{"time":582596,"text":"Now, the thing is,\nthe world is going to need"},{"time":585170,"text":"all of the different kinds of minds\nto work together."},{"time":589283,"text":"We've got to work on developing\nall these different kinds of minds."},{"time":592498,"text":"And one of the things\nthat is driving me really crazy"},{"time":595064,"text":"as I travel around\nand I do autism meetings,"},{"time":597435,"text":"is I'm seeing a lot of smart,\ngeeky, nerdy kids,"},{"time":600600,"text":"and they just aren't very social,"},{"time":602799,"text":"and nobody's working\non developing their interest"},{"time":605914,"text":"in something like science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":607666,"text":"And this brings up the whole thing\nof my science teacher."},{"time":610377,"text":"My science teacher is shown\nabsolutely beautifully in the movie."},{"time":613509,"text":"I was a goofball student\nwhen I was in high school."},{"time":616019,"text":"I just didn't care at all about studying,"},{"time":618071,"text":"until I had Mr. Carlock's science class."},{"time":621324,"text":"He was now Dr. Carlock in the movie."},{"time":624097,"text":"And he got me challenged\nto figure out an optical illusion room."},{"time":630000,"text":"This brings up the whole thing\nof you've got to show kids"},{"time":632739,"text":"interesting stuff."},{"time":634314,"text":"You know, one of the things\nthat I think maybe TED ought to do"},{"time":637651,"text":"is tell all the schools about all\nthe great lectures that are on TED,"},{"time":640990,"text":"and there's all kinds\nof great stuff on the Internet"},{"time":643501,"text":"to get these kids turned on."},{"time":644897,"text":"Because I'm seeing a lot\nof these geeky, nerdy kids,"},{"time":647407,"text":"and the teachers out in the Midwest\nand other parts of the country"},{"time":650615,"text":"when you get away from these tech areas,"},{"time":652577,"text":"they don't know what to do\nwith these kids."},{"time":654613,"text":"And they're not going down the right path."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656658,"text":"The thing is, you can make a mind"},{"time":658464,"text":"to be more of a thinking\nand cognitive mind,"},{"time":661213,"text":"or your mind can be wired\nto be more social."},{"time":663712,"text":"And what some of the research\nnow has shown in autism"},{"time":666367,"text":"is there may by extra wiring back here\nin the really brilliant mind,"},{"time":669861,"text":"and we lose a few social circuits here."},{"time":671798,"text":"It's kind of a trade-off\nbetween thinking and social."},{"time":674773,"text":"And then you can get to the point\nwhere it's so severe,"},{"time":677389,"text":"you're going to have a person\nthat's going to be non-verbal."},{"time":680269,"text":"In the normal human mind,"},{"time":682000,"text":"language covers up the visual thinking\nwe share with animals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685646,"text":"This is the work of Dr. Bruce Miller."},{"time":689496,"text":"He studied Alzheimer's patients\nthat had frontal temporal lobe dementia."},{"time":693252,"text":"And the dementia ate out\nthe language parts of the brain."},{"time":696299,"text":"And then this artwork came out of somebody"},{"time":698594,"text":"who used to install stereos in cars."},{"time":701567,"text":"Now, Van Gogh doesn't know\nanything about physics,"},{"time":705257,"text":"but I think it's very interesting\nthat there was some work done"},{"time":708602,"text":"to show that this eddy pattern\nin this painting"},{"time":711349,"text":"followed a statistical model\nof turbulence,"},{"time":714521,"text":"which brings up the whole interesting idea"},{"time":716564,"text":"of maybe some of this mathematical\npatterns is in our own head."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720326,"text":"And the Wolfram stuff --"},{"time":721903,"text":"I was taking notes and writing down\nall the search words I could use,"},{"time":726493,"text":"because I think that's going to go on\nin my autism lectures."},{"time":729844,"text":"We've got to show\nthese kids interesting stuff."},{"time":732295,"text":"And they've taken out the auto-shop class"},{"time":734586,"text":"and the drafting class and the art class."},{"time":736710,"text":"I mean, art was my best subject in school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":739000,"text":"We've got to think about all\nthese different kinds of minds,"},{"time":741883,"text":"and we've got to absolutely\nwork with these kind of minds,"},{"time":744687,"text":"because we absolutely are going to need"},{"time":746999,"text":"these kinds of people in the future."},{"time":750000,"text":"And let's talk about jobs."},{"time":752264,"text":"OK, my science teacher got me studying,"},{"time":754481,"text":"because I was a goofball\nthat didn't want to study."},{"time":756919,"text":"But you know what?\nI was getting work experience."},{"time":759288,"text":"I'm seeing too many of these smart kids\nwho haven't learned basic things,"},{"time":762776,"text":"like how to be on time -- I was taught\nthat when I was eight years old."},{"time":766248,"text":"How to have table manners\nat granny's Sunday party."},{"time":768827,"text":"I was taught that\nwhen I was very, very young."},{"time":771486,"text":"And when I was 13, I had a job\nat a dressmaker's shop sewing clothes."},{"time":776487,"text":"I did internships in college,"},{"time":779099,"text":"I was building things,"},{"time":782326,"text":"and I also had to learn\nhow to do assignments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":785367,"text":"You know, all I wanted to do was draw\npictures of horses when I was little."},{"time":788981,"text":"My mother said, \"Well let's do\na picture of something else.\""},{"time":791833,"text":"They've got to learn\nhow to do something else."},{"time":794021,"text":"Let's say the kid is fixated on Legos."},{"time":795889,"text":"Let's get him working\non building different things."},{"time":798610,"text":"The thing about the autistic mind\nis it tends to be fixated."},{"time":802230,"text":"Like if the kid loves race cars,\nlet's use race cars for math."},{"time":806132,"text":"Let's figure out how long it takes\na race car to go a certain distance."},{"time":809596,"text":"In other words, use that fixation"},{"time":812733,"text":"in order to motivate that kid,\nthat's one of the things we need to do."},{"time":816613,"text":"I really get fed up when the teachers,"},{"time":819725,"text":"especially when you get away\nfrom this part of the country,"},{"time":822551,"text":"they don't know what to do\nwith these smart kids."},{"time":824955,"text":"It just drives me crazy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826142,"text":"What can visual thinkers\ndo when they grow up?"},{"time":828408,"text":"They can do graphic design,\nall kinds of stuff with computers,"},{"time":831381,"text":"photography, industrial design."},{"time":836383,"text":"The pattern thinkers -- they're the ones\nthat are going to be your mathematicians,"},{"time":840339,"text":"your software engineers,\nyour computer programmers,"},{"time":842870,"text":"all of those kinds of jobs."},{"time":844857,"text":"And then you've got the word minds;\nthey make great journalists,"},{"time":848453,"text":"and they also make really,\nreally good stage actors."},{"time":851000,"text":"Because the thing about being autistic is,"},{"time":853416,"text":"I had to learn social skills\nlike being in a play."},{"time":856271,"text":"You just kind of ...\nyou just have to learn it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":859000,"text":"And we need to be working\nwith these students."},{"time":862000,"text":"And this brings up mentors."},{"time":864132,"text":"You know, my science teacher\nwas not an accredited teacher."},{"time":867256,"text":"He was a NASA space scientist."},{"time":869000,"text":"Some states now are getting it to where,\nif you have a degree in biology"},{"time":872428,"text":"or in chemistry,"},{"time":873723,"text":"you can come into the school\nand teach biology or chemistry."},{"time":876584,"text":"We need to be doing that."},{"time":878540,"text":"Because what I'm observing is,"},{"time":880354,"text":"the good teachers,\nfor a lot of these kids,"},{"time":882427,"text":"are out in the community colleges."},{"time":884099,"text":"But we need to be getting\nsome of these good teachers"},{"time":886659,"text":"into the high schools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":887834,"text":"Another thing that can be very,\nvery, very successful is:"},{"time":891414,"text":"there's a lot of people\nthat may have retired"},{"time":893546,"text":"from working in the software industry,"},{"time":895392,"text":"and they can teach your kid."},{"time":896804,"text":"And it doesn't matter\nif what they teach them is old,"},{"time":899637,"text":"because what you're doing\nis you're lighting the spark."},{"time":902388,"text":"You're getting that kid turned on."},{"time":904876,"text":"And you get him turned on,\nthen you'll learn all the new stuff."},{"time":908315,"text":"Mentors are just essential."},{"time":910603,"text":"I cannot emphasize enough\nwhat my science teacher did for me."},{"time":914944,"text":"And we've got to mentor them, hire them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":918000,"text":"And if you bring them in\nfor internships in your companies,"},{"time":920832,"text":"the thing about the autism,\nAsperger-y kind of mind,"},{"time":923329,"text":"you've got to give them a specific task."},{"time":925321,"text":"Don't just say, \"Design new software.\""},{"time":927187,"text":"You've got to tell them\nsomething more specific:"},{"time":929478,"text":"\"We're designing software for a phone"},{"time":931399,"text":"and it has to do some specific thing,"},{"time":933223,"text":"and it can only use so much memory.\""},{"time":935000,"text":"That's the kind of specificity you need."}]},{"cues":[{"time":937451,"text":"Well, that's the end of my talk."},{"time":939334,"text":"And I just want to thank\neverybody for coming."},{"time":941601,"text":"It was great to be here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":943000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":954526,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":956741,"text":"Oh -- you have a question for me? OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":958590,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":961011,"text":"Chris Anderson:\nThank you so much for that."},{"time":963063,"text":"You know, you once wrote --\nI like this quote:"},{"time":965413,"text":"\"If by some magic, autism had been\neradicated from the face of the Earth,"},{"time":969998,"text":"then men would still be socializing\nin front of a wood fire"},{"time":972999,"text":"at the entrance to a cave.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":974364,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":975416,"text":"Temple Grandin: Because who do you think\nmade the first stone spear?"},{"time":978676,"text":"It was the Asperger guy,"},{"time":979858,"text":"and if you were to get rid\nof all the autism genetics,"},{"time":982435,"text":"there'd be no more Silicon Valley,\nand the energy crisis would not be solved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":986124,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":987489,"text":"CA: I want to ask you\na couple other questions,"},{"time":989743,"text":"and if any of these feel inappropriate,\nit's OK just to say, \"Next question.\""},{"time":993531,"text":"But if there is someone here\nwho has an autistic child,"},{"time":997169,"text":"or knows an autistic child and feels\nkind of cut off from them,"},{"time":1002533,"text":"what advice would you give them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1004404,"text":"TG: Well, first of all,\nwe've got to look at age."},{"time":1006757,"text":"If you have a two, three or four-year-old,\nno speech, no social interaction,"},{"time":1010730,"text":"I can't emphasize enough: Don't wait."},{"time":1013043,"text":"You need at least 20 hours a week\nof one-to-one teaching."},{"time":1016352,"text":"The thing is, autism comes\nin different degrees."},{"time":1018869,"text":"About half of the people on the spectrum\nare not going to learn to talk,"},{"time":1022400,"text":"and they won't be working\nin Silicon Valley."},{"time":1024525,"text":"That would not be a reasonable\nthing for them to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1026999,"text":"But then you get these smart,\ngeeky kids with a touch of autism,"},{"time":1030100,"text":"and that's where you've got\nto get them turned on"},{"time":1032604,"text":"with doing interesting things."},{"time":1034117,"text":"I got social interaction\nthrough shared interests --"},{"time":1037156,"text":"I rode horses with other kids,\nI made model rockets with other kids,"},{"time":1041137,"text":"did electronics lab with other kids."},{"time":1043139,"text":"And in the '60s, it was gluing mirrors\nonto a rubber membrane on a speaker"},{"time":1047414,"text":"to make a light show."},{"time":1048619,"text":"That was, like,\nwe considered that super cool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1050865,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1051895,"text":"CA: Is it unrealistic for them"},{"time":1053416,"text":"to hope or think that that child\nloves them, as some might, as most, wish?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1058180,"text":"TG: Well, I tell you,\nthat child will be loyal,"},{"time":1060438,"text":"and if your house is burning down,\nthey're going to get you out of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1063837,"text":"CA: Wow. So most people, if you ask them\nwhat they're most passionate about,"},{"time":1067520,"text":"they'd say things like,\n\"My kids\" or \"My lover.\""},{"time":1071010,"text":"What are you most passionate about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072786,"text":"TG: I'm passionate\nabout that the things I do"},{"time":1075841,"text":"are going to make\nthe world a better place."},{"time":1077902,"text":"When I have a mother\nof an autistic child say,"},{"time":1080148,"text":"\"My kid went to college\nbecause of your book"},{"time":1082234,"text":"or one of your lectures,\""},{"time":1083458,"text":"that makes me happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1084633,"text":"You know, the slaughter plants\nI worked with in the '80s;"},{"time":1087370,"text":"they were absolutely awful."},{"time":1088711,"text":"I developed a really simple\nscoring system for slaughter plants,"},{"time":1092011,"text":"where you just measure outcomes:"},{"time":1093587,"text":"How many cattle fell down?"},{"time":1094853,"text":"How many got poked with the prodder?"},{"time":1096625,"text":"How many cattle\nare mooing their heads off?"},{"time":1099018,"text":"And it's very, very simple."},{"time":1100376,"text":"You directly observe a few simple things."},{"time":1102377,"text":"It's worked really well."},{"time":1103565,"text":"I get satisfaction out of seeing stuff"},{"time":1105928,"text":"that makes real change in the real world."},{"time":1108672,"text":"We need a lot more of that,\nand a lot less abstract stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1111445,"text":"CA: Totally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1112620,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1117727,"text":"CA: When we were talking on the phone,\none of the things you said"},{"time":1120850,"text":"that really astonished me"},{"time":1122076,"text":"was that one thing you were passionate\nabout was server farms."},{"time":1125843,"text":"Tell me about that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1127018,"text":"TG: Well, the reason why I got really\nexcited when I read about that,"},{"time":1130419,"text":"it contains knowledge."},{"time":1132099,"text":"It's libraries."},{"time":1133781,"text":"And to me, knowledge is something\nthat is extremely valuable."},{"time":1137324,"text":"So, maybe over 10 years ago\nnow, our library got flooded."},{"time":1140464,"text":"This is before the Internet\ngot really big."},{"time":1142539,"text":"And I was really upset\nabout all the books being wrecked,"},{"time":1145244,"text":"because it was knowledge being destroyed."},{"time":1147244,"text":"And server farms, or data centers,\nare great libraries of knowledge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1151681,"text":"CA: Temple, can I just say,"},{"time":1152996,"text":"it's an absolute delight\nto have you at TED."},{"time":1155106,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1156281,"text":"TG: Well, thank you so much. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1158200,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}